      "title": "GMOA wants proper program for health service",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); The Government Medical Officers\u2019 Association (GMOA) says that a system should be prepared for doctors, and all health staff, to report to the hospitals with the current fuel crisis in the country.",
        "The Chairman of the GMOA Dr. Dharshana Sirisena said that a discussion will be held with the Minister of Health on Tuesday (28) afternoon regarding the matter.",
        "BREAKING: Only essential services to operate from midnight (27); CPC will only issue fuel for essential services"
      ],
